root: ^*After picking up this little, pink note, strange visions hit you. You see a distorted picture, like if you were watching it from behind a glass of water.*

^*Stephen standing next to Astira. The vision blurs. A woman in a long, black dress. Joe. She discreetly puts a small note into a pocket of the Prince’s suit and leaves. You see high heels stepping on a bloody floor and come back to your senses.*
